# Task #128: the Game Manager's SYSTEM PICKER must not list the Game Manager's own
# root-entry folder (managing it from inside itself is nonsense, and "Delete from
# card" on it would be refused by the engine anyway). Proof of ABSENCE: the sim's
# minui-list stub exit-43s when a scenario picks a line that is NOT in the drawn
# list — so deliberately picking the GM folder must produce SELECTION NOT IN LIST.
desc Game Manager: its own root-entry folder is absent from the system picker
config paired
seeded
sdfile Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
pick 0|Game Manager
pick 0|Game Manager (LODORGM)
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace SELECTION NOT IN LIST: 'Game Manager (LODORGM)'
